  "tests/fixtures/contracts/full.json:regenerated without extension-contributed entries",project,null
close_reason: Closed at creation via pm create
body: "## Defect\nBoth main pushes on 2026-07-10 failed the Gates (static) job at contracts-snapshot --check: bac1c4c7 because changelog:pm:install refreshed vendored pm-changelog 2026.7.8 -> 2026.7.10 (its contributed contracts changed, fixture diff at line 1324), and 21a7d884 because the vendored copy was untracked entirely (diff at line 34). The gate's purpose is catching unintentional contract drift in THIS repo's CLI/SDK; extension-contributed contracts belong to the extension's own repo and vary by environment, so snapshotting them made the gate nondeterministic.\n\n## Fix\nscripts/contracts-snapshot.mjs now invokes pm --no-extensions contracts --full --json; fixture regenerated (-825 lines of extension entries). Verified: --check passes byte-identically with the extension installed and with it absent."
